Pre-operative checklist

1. Procedure:
   - Epidermal Cyst Excision
   - Pilar cyst Excision
   - Lipoma Excision

2. Site:
   - Scalp
   - Chest/Abdomen
   - Back
   - Upper Extremity
   - Lower Extremity

3. Scalpel:
   - 15-Blade
   - 11-Blade
   - 10-Blade

4. Top Suture:
   - 3-0 Prolene (Polypropylene)
   - 4-0 Prolene (Polypropylene)
   - 5-0 Prolene (Polypropylene)
   - 5-0 Fast Gut
   - Other:**\_**

5. Deep Suture:
   - None
   - 3-0 Vicryl (Polyglactin 910)
   - 4-0 Vicryl (Polyglactin 910)
   - 5-0 Vicryl (Polyglactin 910)
   - 3-0 Monocryl (Poliglecaprone 25)
   - 4-0 Monocryl (Poliglecaprone 25)
   - 5-0 Monocryl (Poliglecaprone 25)
   - other:**\_**

6. Tools:
   - Needle Driver
   - Adson Tissue Forceps
   - Bishop-Harmon Forceps
   - Iris Scissors
   - Wescott/Castroviejo Scissors
   - Undermining Scissors
   - Hemostat
   - Skin Hooks
   - Other:**\_**

7. Patient Position:
   - Supine
   - Prone
   - Trendelenburg
   - Reverse Trendelenburg
   - On left side
   - On right side

8. Top Stiches
   - Simple Interrupted
   - Simple Running
   - Horizontal Mattress
   - Vertical Mattress
   - Other:**\_**
